articles.author: AFP
articles.title: Natural immunity more potent than vaccines during US Delta wave: Study - New Straits Times
articles.description: WASHINGTON: During America's last surge of the coronavirus driven by the Delta variant, people who were unvaccinated but survived Covid were better protected than those who were vaccinated and not previously infected, a new study said Wednesday.
